<div id="post-272071" class="blog-post position-9 odd-post"><div class="odd-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/paulomarcos/blog/reportagem-educacao-arte-e-cultura-na-sala-de-aula-e-nas-ruas-paulo-marcos">Reportagem: Educação, Arte e Cultura na sala de aula e nas ruas - Paulo Marcos</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">Novembre 19, 2010 0:00</span><span class="author">, by Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/paulomarcos/blog/reportagem-educacao-arte-e-cultura-na-sala-de-aula-e-nas-ruas-paulo-marcos#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a></span></span><div>
